    "At h0 under the core-deposit-proximate shock, the closest cross-scope transaction bridge is `strict_di_loans_nec_nonfinancial_corporate_qoq` with beta \u2248 20.82 against DI aggregate \u2248 17.58.",
    "The closest same-scope proxy slice is `loans_to_nondepository_financial_institutions_qoq` with beta \u2248 5.13, but it remains a proxy-level level-change family rather than a clean lender-side transaction split.",
    "So the current public data do not support promoting any DI-loans-n.e.c. subcomponent into the strict object: the exact same-scope transaction subcomponent is unavailable, the best bridges are cross-scope, and the best same-scope slices are proxy-only."
